      <tag>hexo</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>部门工资前三高的所有员工</title>
    <link href="/2024/07/30/hexo%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%20%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%20%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%20%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%20%E5%BD%92%E6%A1%A3/"/>
    <url>/2024/07/30/hexo%E8%AE%BE%E7%BD%AE%20%E5%85%B3%E4%BA%8E%20%E6%A0%87%E7%AD%BE%20%E5%88%86%E7%B1%BB%20%E5%BD%92%E6%A1%A3/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="部门工资前三高的所有员工"><a href="#部门工资前三高的所有员工" class="headerlink" title="部门工资前三高的所有员工"></a>部门工资前三高的所有员工</h1><p>表: <code>Employee</code></p><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><span class="hljs-code">+--------------+</span>---------+<br><span class="hljs-section">| Column Name  | Type    |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+--------------+---------+</span><br>| id           | int     |<br>| name         | varchar |<br>| salary       | int     |<br><span class="hljs-section">| departmentId | int     |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+--------------+---------+</span><br>id 是该表的主键列(具有唯一值的列)。<br>departmentId 是 Department 表中 ID 的外键（reference 列）。<br>该表的每一行都表示员工的ID、姓名和工资。它还包含了他们部门的ID。<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>表: <code>Department</code></p><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc"><span class="hljs-code">+-------------+</span>---------+<br><span class="hljs-section">| Column Name | Type    |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+-------------+---------+</span><br>| id          | int     |<br><span class="hljs-section">| name        | varchar |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+-------------+---------+</span><br>id 是该表的主键列(具有唯一值的列)。<br>该表的每一行表示部门ID和部门名。<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>公司的主管们感兴趣的是公司每个部门中谁赚的钱最多。一个部门的 <strong>高收入者</strong> 是指一个员工的工资在该部门的 <strong>不同</strong> 工资中 <strong>排名前三</strong> 。</p><p>编写解决方案，找出每个部门中 <strong>收入高的员工</strong> 。</p><p>以 <strong>任意顺序</strong> 返回结果表。</p><p>返回结果格式如下所示。</p><p>示例 1:</p><figure class="highlight asciidoc"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs asciidoc">输入: <br><span class="hljs-section">Employee 表:</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+----+-------+--------+--------------+</span><br><span class="hljs-section">| id | name  | salary | departmentId |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+----+-------+--------+--------------+</span><br>| 1  | Joe   | 85000  | 1            |<br>| 2  | Henry | 80000  | 2            |<br>| 3  | Sam   | 60000  | 2            |<br>| 4  | Max   | 90000  | 1            |<br>| 5  | Janet | 69000  | 1            |<br>| 6  | Randy | 85000  | 1            |<br><span class="hljs-section">| 7  | Will  | 70000  | 1            |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+----+-------+--------+--------------+</span><br><span class="hljs-section">Department  表:</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+----+-------+</span><br><span class="hljs-section">| id | name  |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+----+-------+</span><br>| 1  | IT    |<br><span class="hljs-section">| 2  | Sales |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+----+-------+</span><br><span class="hljs-section">输出: </span><br><span class="hljs-section">+------------+----------+--------+</span><br><span class="hljs-section">| Department | Employee | Salary |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+------------+----------+--------+</span><br>| IT         | Max      | 90000  |<br>| IT         | Joe      | 85000  |<br>| IT         | Randy    | 85000  |<br>| IT         | Will     | 70000  |<br>| Sales      | Henry    | 80000  |<br><span class="hljs-section">| Sales      | Sam      | 60000  |</span><br><span class="hljs-section">+------------+----------+--------+</span><br>解释:<br>在IT部门:<br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>Max的工资最高<br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>兰迪和乔都赚取第二高的独特的薪水<br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>威尔的薪水是第三高的<br><br>在销售部:<br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>亨利的工资最高<br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>山姆的薪水第二高<br><span class="hljs-bullet">- </span>没有第三高的工资，因为只有两名员工<br><br><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>解决方案</strong></p><figure class="highlight coq"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br><span class="line">69</span><br><span class="line">70</span><br><span class="line">71</span><br><span class="line">72</span><br><span class="line">73</span><br><span class="line">74</span><br><span class="line">75</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs coq">​```<br>select Department ,Employee ,Salary  from  （select b.name <span class="hljs-built_in">as</span> Department,a.name <span class="hljs-built_in">as</span> Employee,a.SALARY, <br>DENSE_RANK() OVER(PARTITION BY b.name ORDER BY a.SALARY desc) <span class="hljs-built_in">as</span>  SALARY_rank<br>from  Employee  a<br>LEFT JOIN Department  b ON a.departmentId =b.id ）<br>WHERE SALARY_rank&lt;=<span class="hljs-number">3</span>  order <span class="hljs-built_in">by</span>  Department,Salary desc<br>​```<br>通过<br>执行用时: <span class="hljs-number">687</span> ms<br>Case <span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>输入<br>Employee =<br>| <span class="hljs-type">id</span> | <span class="hljs-type">name</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">salary</span> | <span class="hljs-type">departmentId</span> |<br><span class="hljs-type">| -- | ----- | ------ | ------------ |</span><br><span class="hljs-type">| 1</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">Joe</span>   | <span class="hljs-type">85000</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">1</span>            |<br><span class="hljs-type">| 2</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">Henry</span> | <span class="hljs-type">80000</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">2</span>            |<br><span class="hljs-type">| 3</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">Sam</span>   | <span class="hljs-type">60000</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">2</span>            |<br><span class="hljs-type">| 4</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">Max</span>   | <span class="hljs-type">90000</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">1</span>            |<br><span class="hljs-type">| 5</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">Janet</span> | <span class="hljs-type">69000</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">1</span>            |<br><span class="hljs-type">| 6</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">Randy</span> | <span class="hljs-type">85000</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">1</span>            |<br><span class="hljs-type">查看更多</span><br><span class="hljs-type">Department</span> =<br>| <span class="hljs-type">id</span> | <span class="hljs-type">name</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| -- | ----- |</span><br><span class="hljs-type">| 1</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">IT</span>    |<br><span class="hljs-type">| 2</span>  | <span class="hljs-type">Sales</span> |<br><span class="hljs-type">输出</span><br><span class="hljs-type">| DEPARTMENT</span> | <span class="hljs-type">EMPLOYEE</span> | <span class="hljs-type">SALARY</span> |<br><span class="hljs-type">| ---------- | -------- | ------ |</span><br><span class="hljs-type">| IT</span>         | <span class="hljs-type">Max</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">90000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| IT</span>         | <span class="hljs-type">Randy</span>    | <span class="hljs-type">85000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| IT</span>         | <span class="hljs-type">Joe</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">85000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| IT</span>         | <span class="hljs-type">Will</span>     | <span class="hljs-type">70000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| Sales</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">Henry</span>    | <span class="hljs-type">80000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| Sales</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">Sam</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">60000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">预期结果</span><br><span class="hljs-type">| Department</span> | <span class="hljs-type">Employee</span> | <span class="hljs-type">Salary</span> |<br><span class="hljs-type">| ---------- | -------- | ------ |</span><br><span class="hljs-type">| IT</span>         | <span class="hljs-type">Joe</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">85000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| Sales</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">Henry</span>    | <span class="hljs-type">80000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| Sales</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">Sam</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">60000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| IT</span>         | <span class="hljs-type">Max</span>      | <span class="hljs-type">90000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| IT</span>         | <span class="hljs-type">Randy</span>    | <span class="hljs-type">85000</span>  |<br><span class="hljs-type">| IT</span>         | <span class="hljs-type">Will</span>     | <span class="hljs-type">70000</span>  |<br><br><br><span class="hljs-type">DENSE_RANK</span>()详解<br>假设我们有一个学生分数表，表中包含学生的姓名和他们的数学成绩。我们想要基于这些成绩给学生们排名，但如果有两个或多个学生成绩相同，我们希望他们共享同一个排名，并且下一个排名不会跳过任何数字（即不使用间隔排名）。<br><br>学生姓名成绩<br>张三<span class="hljs-number">90</span><br>李四<span class="hljs-number">85</span><br>王五<span class="hljs-number">90</span><br>赵六<span class="hljs-number">80</span><br>钱七<span class="hljs-number">95</span><br><br>如果我们使用DENSE_RANK()函数来基于成绩对学生进行排名，结果将会是这样的：<br><br>学生姓名成绩密集等级<br>张三<span class="hljs-number">90</span><span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>王五<span class="hljs-number">90</span><span class="hljs-number">1</span><br>李四<span class="hljs-number">85</span><span class="hljs-number">2</span><br>赵六<span class="hljs-number">80</span><span class="hljs-number">3</span><br>钱七<span class="hljs-number">95</span><span class="hljs-number">4</span><br><br>解释如下：<br><br>张三和王五的成绩都是<span class="hljs-number">90</span>分，因此他们共享了密集等级<span class="hljs-number">1</span>。<br>接下来是李四，他的成绩是<span class="hljs-number">85</span>分，与前面的<span class="hljs-number">90</span>分不同，所以他的密集等级是<span class="hljs-number">2</span>（没有跳过<span class="hljs-number">1</span>，因为前面有相同的排名）。<br>赵六的成绩是<span class="hljs-number">80</span>分，与前面的都不同，所以他得到了下一个连续的密集等级<span class="hljs-number">3</span>。<br>最后，钱七的成绩是<span class="hljs-number">95</span>分，这是目前为止最高的成绩，所以他得到了下一个连续的密集等级<span class="hljs-number">4</span>。<br>通过这个例子，我们可以看到DENSE_RANK()函数如何确保即使在有相同排序值的情况下，也能保持密集等级的连续性，不会跳过任何数字。这与使用RANK()函数不同，后者在遇到相同排序值时可能会跳过某些排名（因为RANK()在遇到相同值时，会给相同值的行分配相同的排名，但下一个不同值的行会跳过已经使用过的排名）。<br><br><br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
